WEBVTT

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:38.160
<v LastAir>Ok so. Shared Hallucination. Welcome back. I'm your host, LastAir. And tonight we finally get to the episode I've been putting off. Because I couldn't figure out how to look at it straight. (pause) At the table tonight: Hex, who I'm told has been sitting on an extremely organized list of opinions.</v>

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:44.480
